for the Minneapolis Housing Authority, Housing

00:33.899 --> 00:45.213
Redevelopment Authority, in Minneapolis as a 
planner. Then went on to the New York State Urban

00:45.233 --> 01:02.235
Development Corporation as a project manager, 
