that an urbanizing population required, had 
become

27:08.924 --> 27:26.023
bastions of the white middle class, and they were 
not integrated. And there were a number of the

27:27.004 --> 27:37.395
developers who wanted to show that you could 
create cities that would not be

27:39.518 --> 27:46.026
full of the problems, replete with the problems of 
the older cities. So you had George Mitchell,

27:46.486 --> 27:48.629
Huber, and several others. Lester Gross and 
Harbison. OK, so you had your for-profit, the

27:51.172 --> 27:55.096
profit-motivated. Then you had your 
